            {
              "content": "=You are a lead qualification assistant. \nGiven this product data, give it a quality score from 1-10 \nand a one sentence summary explaining why it's worth attention.\n\nProduct Name: {{ $json.name }}\nPrice: {{ $json.price }}\nRating: {{ $json.rating }}\n\nRespond in this exact format:\nScore: [number]\nSummary: [one sentence]"
